# Quantumult X RuleSet - china.list (host-suffix / host)
# Repo: Jovanykoch/Jovanykoch.github.io
# Updated: 2026-04-03
#
# Usage (Quantumult X):
# [filter_remote]
# https://jkoch14.me/qx/china.list, tag=china.list, force-policy=DIRECT, update-interval=86400, opt-parser=false, enabled=true

# --- Mainland China TLDs ---
host-suffix,cn
host-suffix,xn--fiqs8s
host-suffix,xn--55qx5d
